\id 1JN New Alpha - June 11, 2007
\h 1 JUAN
\toc3 1Jn
\toc2 1 Juan
\toc1 RI NABꞌE WUJ RI XUTZꞌIBꞌAJ RI JUAN
\mt1 RI NABꞌE WUJ RI XUTZꞌIBꞌAJ RI JUAN
\imt2 Majibꞌal re
\ip We wuj riꞌ ubꞌiꞌnam nabꞌe Juan xtaq bꞌik chike jupuq winaq e kojonelabꞌ ri e kꞌo pa jun kꞌulmatajik ri man qas ta kꞌyaqalik. E kꞌo jujun chike xkitzaq kan ri kikojobꞌal che ri Jesús rumal che ri xkꞌut chikiwach chi ri Dios xpe pa tyoꞌjal we kꞌutuꞌn riꞌ man kajunumataj ta rukꞌ ri kichomanik ri winaq aꞌj Grecia ri kubꞌij chi ri utyoꞌjal ri winaq itzel wi, xwi ri ruxlabꞌal utz. Pune jeriꞌ, man kakikoj taj chi kꞌo ri Mesías, xaq mak kakilij ubꞌanik, kakitzijoj rij ri loqꞌanik xuqujeꞌ kakibꞌij chi ketaꞌm uwach ri Dios xuqujeꞌ e rech ri Dios. Kakibꞌij chi ri kakil aꞌreꞌ pa ri uxlabꞌal kubꞌan chike chi e kꞌo na chikiwach ri e kachiꞌl are waꞌ xkikꞌutu are xkitzaq kanoq ri kikojobꞌal.
\ip Ri xekanaj kanoq sibꞌalaj xexibꞌixkanoq man qas ta kꞌyaqalik ri xkꞌut chikiwach. Rumal waꞌ jun chike ri winaq qas xril ri Jesús xutzꞌibꞌaj chike ri winaq ronojel ri kitom loq pa ri majibꞌal re ronojel.
\ip Ri tzꞌibꞌal re we wuj ri man kuqꞌalajisaj taj jas ri ubꞌiꞌ xa kꞌu tzi qꞌalaj chi are ri taqoꞌn Juan jeriꞌ rumal ronojel ri tzij ri kubꞌij kajunumataj rukꞌ ri wuj re ri utz laj tzij re Juan.
\ip Ri wuj kuqꞌalajisaj chi ri Mesías xpe pa tyoꞌjal xuqujeꞌ kukꞌyaqabꞌa ubꞌixik chike ri kojonelabꞌ chi aꞌreꞌ etaꞌmaninaq ri qas tzij.
\ip Kꞌisbꞌal re kubꞌij jas rajawaxik kenoꞌjin ri ketaꞌm uwach ri Dios.
\c 1
\s1 Ri tzij ri kuya kꞌaslemal
\p 
\v 1 Ri kꞌo wi loq are majoꞌq katik ronojel ri jastaq, ri xqato, ri xqil rukꞌ ri qabꞌoqꞌoch, ri qas xqachap rukꞌ ri qaqꞌabꞌ, ri tzij ri kuya kꞌaslemal, are waꞌ ri kaqatzijoj chiꞌwe.
\v 2 We kꞌaslemal riꞌ xukꞌut ribꞌ chiqawach rumal waꞌ kaqatzijoj xuqujeꞌ kaqaqꞌalajisaj chiꞌwe ri jun alik kꞌaslemal ri ojer kꞌo rukꞌ ri Tataxel Dios.
\v 3 Kaqatzijoj chiꞌwe ri xqilo xuqujeꞌ xqato rech kꞌo qariqoj ibꞌ iwukꞌ, xuqujeꞌ rukꞌ ri Tataxel Dios, rachiꞌl ri ukꞌojol Jesucristo.
\v 4 Kaqatzꞌibꞌaj we jastaq riꞌ chiꞌwe rech qas katzꞌaqat ri qakiꞌkotemal.
\s1 Chujbꞌinoq pa ri tunal
\p 
\v 5 Are waꞌ ri tzij ri xubꞌij ri Cristo chaqe, rumal riꞌ kaqatzijoj chiꞌwe: Ri Dios are tunal, maj qꞌequꞌmal rukꞌ Areꞌ.
\v 6 We kaqabꞌij chi kꞌo qariqoj ibꞌ rukꞌ ri Cristo kꞌa te riꞌ xaq jeꞌ uj kꞌo pa ri qꞌequꞌmal, xaq uj bꞌanal taq tzij riꞌ, man tajin ta kaqanimaj ri Dios.
\v 7 We uj kꞌo pa ri tunal, jacha ri Cristo kꞌo pa ri tunal, kꞌo qariqoj ibꞌ riꞌ kukꞌ nikꞌaj chik, xuqujeꞌ ri ukikꞌel ri Cristo, ukꞌojol ri Dios are kujchꞌajchꞌobꞌen che ronojel uwach mak.
\p 
\v 8 We kaqabꞌij chi maj qamak, uj bꞌanal taq tzij riꞌ, man uj kꞌo ta riꞌ pa ri qas tzij.
\v 9 We kaqatzujuj qibꞌ che ri qamak, ri Dios ri sibꞌalaj sukꞌ ri kubꞌano ri kubꞌij, kujukuy na xuqujeꞌ kujuchꞌajchꞌobꞌej na che ronojel uwach etzelal.
\v 10 We kaqabꞌij chi man uj makuninaq taj, tajin kaqabꞌij riꞌ chi ri Dios xaq bꞌanal tzij, xuqujeꞌ man kꞌo ta riꞌ ri utzij pa qanimaꞌ.
\c 2
\p 
\v 1 Loqꞌalaj taq walkꞌwaꞌl, kintzꞌibꞌaj we jastaq riꞌ chiꞌwe rech man kixmakun taj. We kꞌu ne kꞌo jun kamakun chiꞌwe, kꞌo jun chꞌawenel pa qawiꞌ choch ri Tataxel Dios, are ri Jesucristo ri sukꞌ.
\v 2 Are ri Jesucristo xya pa kamikal rumal ri qamak, man xaq xwi taj rumal ri qamak uj xane xkam xuqujeꞌ rumal ri kimak konojel ri winaq choch ri uwachulew.
\p 
\v 3 Qetaꞌm uwach riꞌ ri Dios we kaqanimaj ri utaqanik.
\v 4 Ri winaq ri kubꞌij wetaꞌm uwach ri Dios, kꞌa te riꞌ man kunimaj taj ri utaqanik, xaq bꞌanal tzij, man retaꞌm taj uwach riꞌ ri qas tzij.
\v 5 Are kꞌu ri uloqꞌanik ri Dios kukꞌut ribꞌ pa ri winaq ri kunimaj ri utz laj tzij. Are waꞌ kakꞌutuwik chi xa jun qaꞌnik rukꞌ ri Dios.
\v 6 Ri winaq ri kubꞌij chi kꞌo pa Cristo, rajawaxik je kanoꞌjinik jetaq ri xnoꞌjin areꞌ.
\p 
\v 7 Loqꞌalaj taq wachalal, man jun kꞌakꞌ taqanik taj ri kintzꞌibꞌaj chiꞌwe, xane ojer chik yaꞌtal loq chiꞌwe. We ojer taqanik riꞌ are ri utzij ri Dios ri xitatabꞌej.
\v 8 Xuqujeꞌ kintzꞌibꞌaj chiꞌwe jun kꞌakꞌ taqanik riꞌ ri kakꞌulmataj na pa Cristo xuqujeꞌ pa taq ri ikꞌaslemal ix, jeriꞌ rumal tajin kasach uwach ri qꞌequꞌmal are tajin katunan chik ri tunal.
\p 
\v 9 Ri winaq ri kubꞌij chi kꞌo pa ri tunal kꞌa te riꞌ karetzelaj uwach ri rachalal, riꞌ pa ri qꞌequꞌmal ri kꞌo wi.
\v 10 Ri winaq ri kuloqꞌaj ri rachalal pa ri tunal riꞌ kꞌo wiꞌ, maj jun jastaq kaqꞌaten na pa ri ukꞌaslemal.
\v 11 Ri karetzelaj ri rachalal, kꞌo ri pa ri qꞌequꞌmal, pa ri qꞌequꞌmal riꞌ kꞌo wi rachoch, man retaꞌm ta riꞌ jawjeꞌ keꞌ wi, rumal ri qꞌequꞌmal karil ta ri ubꞌe.
\p 
\v 12 Kintzꞌibꞌaj we wuj riꞌ chiꞌwe ix alkꞌwaꞌlaxelabꞌ rumal xkuyutaj ri imak pa ri ubꞌiꞌ ri Cristo.
\v 13 Kintzꞌibꞌaj we wuj riꞌ chiꞌwe ix tat nan rumal cher iwetaꞌm loq uwach ri Cristo kꞌo wi loq pa ri majibꞌal rech ronojel. Kintzꞌibꞌaj xuqujeꞌ chiꞌwe ix akꞌal taq alabꞌom, akꞌal taq alitomabꞌ rumal cher xichꞌek ri itzel.
\v 14 Kintzꞌibꞌaj chiꞌwe ix tat nan, rumal cher iwetaꞌm uwach ri Dios ri kꞌo wi loq pa ri majibꞌal rech ronojel. Kintzꞌibꞌaj chiꞌwe ix akꞌal taq alabꞌom, akꞌal taq alitomabꞌ rumal cher sibꞌalaj kꞌo ichuqꞌabꞌ xuqujeꞌ ri utzij ri Dios kꞌo pa iwanimaꞌ, xuqujeꞌ xichꞌek ri itzel.
\p 
\v 15 Meꞌ ikꞌuꞌx rukꞌ ri jastaq rech uwachulew. We jachin kuloqꞌaj ri jastaq rech ri uwachulew, man kꞌo ta riꞌ ri uloqꞌanik ri Tataxel Dios pa ranimaꞌ.
\v 16 Ronojel ri jastaq rech uwachulew, ri itzel taq urayinik ri tyoꞌjal, ri jiqꞌjatem ri kukaꞌyej ri bꞌoqꞌochaj, ri nimal ri kunaꞌ jun, man rukꞌ taj ri Tataxel Dios kape wi, xane rech ri uwachulew.
\v 17 Ri itzel taq rayinik rech ri uwachulew kasach na uwach, are kꞌu ri winaq ri kunimaj ri kubꞌij ri Dios, kakꞌasiꞌ na chibꞌe qꞌij saq.
\s1 Kepe na winaq ri kakijaluj chi aꞌreꞌ e Cristo
\p 
\v 18 Loqꞌalaj taq walkꞌwaꞌl, uj kꞌo chi pa ri kꞌisbꞌal taq qꞌij, jetaq ri xitatabꞌej chi kape na ri winaq ri kujaluj chi are Cristo, sibꞌalaj e kꞌi chik ri winaq ri kakijaluj chi aꞌreꞌ e Cristo rumal laꞌ kinbꞌij chiꞌwe chi uj kꞌo pa taq ri kꞌisbꞌal taq qꞌij kamik.
\v 19 Pune we winaq riꞌ qukꞌ xeꞌl wi bꞌik, man kel ta kubꞌij chi e qachiꞌl, we ta e qachiꞌl xekanaj ta kan riꞌ qukꞌ. Xel kꞌu bꞌik qukꞌ rumal man e qachiꞌl taj.
\p 
\v 20 Ri ix kꞌut, xikꞌamawaꞌj ri Tyoxalaj Uxlabꞌixel, rumal riꞌ iwetaꞌm uwach ri qas tzij.
\v 21 Man kintzꞌibꞌaj taj we tzij riꞌ chiꞌwe rumal man iwetaꞌm taj ri qas tzij, xane kintzꞌibꞌaj chiꞌwe rumal iwetaꞌm ri qas tzij xuqujeꞌ rumal maj xa ta ne nitzꞌ bꞌanoj tzij kꞌo pa ri qas tzij.
\p 
\v 22 ¿Jachin kꞌu ri bꞌanal tzij we man are ri winaq ri man kuqꞌalajisaj taj ri Cristo? Ri winaq ri kujaluj chi are Cristo, are riꞌ ri winaq ri man kakojon ta che ri Dios rachiꞌl ri Cristo.
\v 23 Ri man kakojon ta che ri Cristo, ri kꞌojolaxel, man kꞌo ta riꞌ ri Tataxel Dios pa ranimaꞌ, ri kakojon che ri Cristo, kꞌo riꞌ ri Tataxel Dios pa ranimaꞌ.
\p 
\v 24 Kꞌol pa iwanimaꞌ ri kꞌuttal loq chiꞌwach are xmajtaj loq ronojel, rech jeriꞌ kixkꞌojiꞌ pa Dios xuqujeꞌ pa ri ukꞌojol Jesús.
\v 25 Ri ubꞌim kanoq ri Cristo chaqe are ri jun alik kꞌaslemal ri xuya chaqe.
\p 
\v 26 Areꞌ waꞌ ri jastaq ri kintzꞌibꞌaj chiꞌwe rech maj jun kixsubꞌuwik.
\v 27 Xuqujeꞌ ri uxlabꞌal ri xikꞌamawaꞌj che ri Cristo kꞌo chiꞌwe, man rajawaxik ta chik chi jun winaq kakꞌutuw chiꞌwach. Ri uxlabꞌal ri xikꞌamawaꞌj, qas che ri Dios xikꞌamawaꞌj wiꞌ man xaq ta esal uwach, are waꞌ ri kakꞌutuw na chiꞌwach ronojel ri jastaq. Chixjeqel bꞌa pa Cristo jacha ri xukꞌut kanoq chiꞌwach.
\p 
\v 28 Loqꞌalaj taq walkꞌwaꞌl, chixkꞌol bꞌa pa Cristo, rech are kapetik man kubꞌan ta kebꞌ qakꞌuꞌx are kaqakꞌut qibꞌ choch, rech man kel taj qakꞌixibꞌal.
\v 29 We qas kichꞌobꞌo chi ri Jesucristo maj umak, chichꞌobꞌo xuqujeꞌ chi ri winaq ri kubꞌan ri sukꞌal, che ri Cristo petinaq wi.
\c 3
\p 
\v 1 ¡Chiwilampeꞌ! Sibꞌalaj nim ri loqꞌanik ri xuya ri qatat Dios chaqe, rumal riꞌ kubꞌij chi uj ralkꞌwaꞌl, qas uj ralkꞌwaꞌl kꞌu wi, ri winaq ri man e kojonelabꞌ taj man ketaꞌm taj uj jachin uj, jeriꞌ rumal cher man ketaꞌm taj uwach ri Cristo.
\v 2 Loqꞌalaj taq qachalal, uj ralkꞌwaꞌl chi ri Dios kamik, majaꞌ kꞌu kaqꞌalajinik jas qas kujux na. Xwi qetaꞌm chi are kape ri Cristo kujjunumataj na rukꞌ Areꞌ, jeriꞌ rumal kaqil na uwach.
\v 3 Xapachin ri jeqel ukꞌuꞌx pa Cristo man kamakun ta riꞌ jacha ri Cristo man kamakun taj.
\p 
\v 4 Ri winaq ri kubꞌan mak kuqꞌipij ri taqanik; xuqujeꞌ man nimanel taj che.
\v 5 Iwetaꞌm kꞌut chi ri Cristo xpetik chuchupik ri qamak. Xuqujeꞌ Areꞌ man kꞌo ta umak.
\v 6 Ri winaq ri kꞌo pa Cristo man are ta karilij ubꞌanik ri mak. Ri winaq ri are karilij ubꞌanik mak man rilom taj xuqujeꞌ man retaꞌmam ta uwach ri Cristo.
\v 7 Loqꞌalaj taq walkꞌwaꞌl, kꞌo mixsubꞌuwik. Ri winaq ri kubꞌan ri sukꞌal, sukꞌ winaq riꞌ, jetaq ri Cristo.
\v 8 Ri winaq ri are karilij ubꞌanik mak rech ri Itzel riꞌ, jeriꞌ rumal ri Itzel xaq are wi rilim loq ubꞌanik ri mak pa ri majibꞌal rech ronojel. Rumal riꞌ ri Cristo xtaq loq chutukixik ri uchak ri Itzel.
\p 
\v 9 Ri xalax chi junmul pa Cristo man are ta karilij ubꞌanik riꞌ ri mak, jeriꞌ rumal xya jun ijaꞌ rech ri Dios pa ri ukꞌaslemal rech man are ta karilij ubꞌanik ri mak.
\v 10 Jeriꞌ kaqꞌalajinik jachin ri ralkꞌwaꞌl ri Dios xuqujeꞌ jachin ri ralkꞌwaꞌl ri Itzel. Ri man kubꞌan ta ri sukꞌal xuqujeꞌ man kuloqꞌaj taj ri rachalal man ralkꞌwaꞌl ta ri Dios riꞌ.
\s1 Qaloqꞌaj qibꞌ qonojel
\p 
\v 11 Ri utz laj tzij ri itatabꞌem loq pa ri majibꞌal rech ronojel, are chi kaqaloqꞌaj qibꞌ chqajujunal.
\v 12 Man kaqesaj taj uwach ri Caín, are waꞌ ri xuya bꞌe xok ri Itzel che rumal riꞌ xukamisaj ri rachalal Abel. ¿Jas che jewaꞌ xubꞌano? Jeriꞌ xubꞌano rumal are xrilij ubꞌanik itzel taq chak, are kꞌu ri uchak ri rachalal sibꞌalaj utz.\x + \xo 3:12 \xt Génesis 4:8.\x*
\p 
\v 13 Wachalal, man kixmayjan taj we kixketzelaj ri winaq ri man e kojonelabꞌ taj.
\v 14 Qetaꞌm uj chi uj kaminaq kan nabꞌe xa kꞌu xya chi na qakꞌaslemal rumal riꞌ keꞌqaloqꞌaj ri e qachalal. Ri winaq ri man kaloqꞌan taj rech ri kamikal riꞌ.
\v 15 Ri karetzelaj ri rachalal jun kamisanel riꞌ, iwetaꞌm kꞌut chi maj jun kamisanel kakwinik kok pa ri jun alik kꞌaslemal.
\v 16 Ri uj qetaꞌm jas ubꞌanik ri loqꞌanik are chi ri Jesucristo xuya ri ukꞌaslemal rumal qe. Je xuqujeꞌ rajawaxik kaqabꞌan uj, rajawaxik kaqaya ri qakꞌaslemal pa kiwiꞌ ri e qachalal.
\v 17 We kꞌo jun chiꞌwe sibꞌalaj qꞌinom karil kꞌu ri rachalal chi kajawataj ujastaq man kel ta kꞌu ukꞌuꞌx che, man kakwin ta riꞌ kubꞌij chi kꞌo ri loqꞌanik rech ri Dios pa ranimaꞌ.
\v 18 Loqꞌalaj taq walkꞌwaꞌl, man xaq xwi ta kaqabꞌij rukꞌ ri qachiꞌ chi ku qas qakꞌutu rukꞌ ri kaqabꞌano.
\p 
\v 19 Rukꞌ waꞌ qas kaqetaꞌmaj chi uj kꞌo pa ri qas tzij xuqujeꞌ kaqanaꞌo chi utz qaꞌnik cho ri Dios.
\v 20 Pune ri qanimaꞌ man kuqꞌat ta tzij pa qawiꞌ, ri Dios retaꞌm ronojel, areꞌ nim choch ri qanimaꞌ.
\v 21 Loqꞌalaj taq qachalal, we kaqanaꞌo chi ri qanimaꞌ man kuqꞌat ta tzij pa qawiꞌ rumal ri xqabꞌano, kꞌo ukuꞌlibꞌal qakꞌuꞌx riꞌ che ri Dios.
\v 22 Xuqujeꞌ kaqakꞌamawaꞌj na ronojel ri kaqata che ri Dios, jeriꞌ rumal kaqanimaj ri utaqanik xuqujeꞌ kaqabꞌan ri taqalik choch ri Dios.
\v 23 Ri utaqanik ri Dios are chi kujkojon che ri Jesucristo, ri ukꞌojol, xuqujeꞌ kaqaloqꞌaj qibꞌ chiqajujunal, rumal jeriꞌ karaj kaqabꞌano.
\v 24 Ri kunimaj ri uꞌtaqanik ri Dios, qas kꞌo riꞌ pa Dios, xuqujeꞌ ri Dios kꞌo pa ranimaꞌ ri winaq riꞌ. Are ri Uxlabꞌixel ri xuya chaqe kujtoꞌwik chi retaꞌmaxik chi qas kꞌo ri Dios pa qanimaꞌ.
\c 4
\s1 Qakꞌaslebꞌej ri qakꞌaslemal pa ri Uxlabꞌixel
\p 
\v 1 Loqꞌalaj taq qachalal, mikoj rech xapachin ri kubꞌij chiꞌwe chi are ri Uxlabꞌixel kachꞌaw che, xane qas chichꞌobꞌo rij we qas rech ri Dios ri kubꞌij, rumal cher sibꞌalaj e kꞌi winaq xeꞌl loq cho ri uwachulew ri kakijaluj chi e qꞌalajisal taj utzij ri Dios.
\v 2 Ri qꞌalajisal tzij ri kubꞌij chi ri Jesucristo xpe cho ri uwachulew pa tyoꞌjal rech winaq, qas rech wi ri Dios.
\v 3 Ri qꞌalajisal tzij ri kubꞌij chi ri Jesús man rech ta ri Dios, man ralkꞌwaꞌl taj ri Dios riꞌ xane ralkꞌwaꞌl ri esal uwach ri Cristo, itom loq chi ri esal uwach ri Cristo kape na, qas kꞌo chi kꞌu wi choch ri uwachulew.
\p 
\v 4 Loqꞌalaj taq walkꞌwaꞌl, ix ix rech ri Dios xuqujeꞌ xixchꞌeken pa kiwiꞌ ri kakijaluj chi e qꞌalajisal taq utzij ri Dios, jeriꞌ rumal sibꞌalaj nim uchuqꞌabꞌ ri kꞌo iwukꞌ ix, cho ri kꞌo kukꞌ ri winaq ri ajuwachulew.
\v 5 Ri winaq kakitzijoj ri jastaq jetaq ri kakichomaj aꞌreꞌ, rumal cher e rech ri uwachulew xuqujeꞌ ri winaq ajuwachulew utz keꞌkito.
\v 6 Ri uj uj rech ri Dios, konojel ri winaq ri ketaꞌm uwach ri Dios kakitatabꞌej ri kaqabꞌij; ri winaq ri man e rech ta ri Dios man kutatabꞌej ta ri kaqabꞌij. Jeriꞌ kaqabꞌan chi retaꞌmaxik jachin chike ri uxlabꞌal rech ri qas tzij xuqujeꞌ jachin ri uxlabꞌal rech bꞌanal tzij.
\s1 Chujjeqeloq pa ri loqꞌanik
\p 
\v 7 Loqꞌalaj taq qachalal, qaloqꞌaj qibꞌ chiqajujunal, rumal che ri loqꞌanik rukꞌ ri Dios kape wi. Ri winaq ri kaloqꞌanik, retaꞌm uwach ri Dios riꞌ xuqujeꞌ che ri Dios petinaq wi.
\v 8 Jachin ri man kaloqꞌan taj man retaꞌm ta uwach ri Dios riꞌ, jeriꞌ rumal ri Dios areꞌ loqꞌanik.
\v 9 Ri Dios xukꞌut ri uloqꞌanik chiqawach are xutaq loq ri xa jun ukꞌojol cho ri uwachulew rech xa rumal areꞌ kayaꞌtaj na jun alik qakꞌaslemal.
\v 10 Ri loqꞌanik man are taj chi xqaloqꞌaj uj nabꞌe ri Dios, xane Areꞌ xujuloqꞌaj xuqujeꞌ xutaq loq ri xa jun ukꞌojol rech xjach pa kamikal rumal ri qamak.
\p 
\v 11 Loqꞌalaj taq wachalal, we ujuloqꞌam uj ri Dios, qaloqꞌaj xuqujeꞌ qibꞌ uj chiqajujunal.
\v 12 Maj jun ilowinaq ri Dios, we kꞌu kaqaloqꞌaj qibꞌ chiqajujunal kꞌo riꞌ ri Dios pa qanimaꞌ xuqujeꞌ kꞌo riꞌ ri uloqꞌanik chiqaxoꞌl.
\v 13 Ri Uxlabꞌixel ri kꞌo pa qanimaꞌ are kakꞌutuwik chi uj kꞌo pa Cristo xuqujeꞌ ri Cristo kꞌo pa qanimaꞌ.
\v 14 Ri uj xqilo xuqujeꞌ kaqatzijoj chi ri Tataxel Dios xutaq loq ri ukꞌojol chkikolik ri winaq ri e kꞌo cho ri uwachulew.
\v 15 Ri kuqꞌalajisaj chi ri Jesús are ukꞌojol ri Dios, we winaq riꞌ kꞌo pa Dios xuqujeꞌ ri Dios kꞌo pa ranimaꞌ areꞌ.
\p 
\v 16 Ri uj xqetaꞌmaj xuqujeꞌ kaqakojo chi ri Dios kujuloqꞌaj. Ri Dios are loqꞌanik. Ri kꞌo pa loqꞌanik, kꞌo pa Dios xuqujeꞌ ri Dios kꞌo pa ranimaꞌ ri winaq riꞌ.
\v 17 We loqꞌanik riꞌ kukꞌut ribꞌ chiqaxoꞌl uj, rech are kuriq ri qꞌij rech qꞌatoj tzij rukꞌ kuꞌlibꞌal kꞌuꞌx kaqakꞌut qibꞌ choch ri Dios, jeriꞌ rumal xqakꞌaslebꞌej ri qakꞌaslemal jacha ri xnoꞌjin ri Jesús. Pa ri loqꞌanik maj xibꞌin ibꞌ.
\v 18 Xane ri tzꞌaqatalaj loqꞌanik karesaj bꞌi ri xibꞌin ibꞌ. Ri winaq ri xaq kuxiꞌj ribꞌ che ri kꞌax ri kape puꞌwiꞌ, majaꞌ katzꞌaqat riꞌ pa ri loqꞌanik.
\p 
\v 19 Ri uj kaqaloqꞌaj ri Dios jeriꞌ rumal cher Areꞌ xujuloqꞌaj nabꞌe.
\v 20 We kꞌo jun kubꞌij: Ri in kinloqꞌaj ri Dios, karetzelaj kꞌu uwach ri rachalal, xaq jun bꞌanal tzij riꞌ, rumal che ri winaq ri man kuloqꞌaj taj ri rachalal, ri karil uwach ronojel qꞌij, man kakwin ta riꞌ kuloqꞌaj ri Dios ri man rilom ta uwach.
\v 21 Are ri Dios yoꞌwinaq ri taqanik chaqe ri kubꞌij: Ri kuloqꞌaj ri Dios chuloqꞌaj xuqujeꞌ ri rachalal.
\c 5
\s1 Ko chujkꞌol pa ri qakojobꞌal
\p 
\v 1 Ri winaq ri kukojo chi ri Jesús are Cristo che ri Dios kꞌiyinaq wi, xuqujeꞌ ri kuloqꞌaj ri Tataxel Dios kuꞌloqꞌaj xuqujeꞌ ri e ralkꞌwaꞌl ri Dios.
\v 2 Are kaqaloqꞌaj ri Dios xuqujeꞌ kaqanimaj ri utaqanik, qetaꞌm chi tajin keꞌqaloqꞌaj ri e ralkꞌwaꞌl ri Dios.
\v 3 Ri uloqꞌanik ri Dios are chi kaqanimaj ri utaqanik. Man kꞌax ta kꞌut unimaxik.
\v 4 Ri alaxinaq pa Dios kachꞌeken puꞌwiꞌ ri jastaq rech uwachulew. Ri qakojobꞌal kachꞌeken puꞌwiꞌ ri jastaq rech uwachulew. Are waꞌ ri qachꞌekoj.
\v 5 Ri winaq ri kukojo chi ri Jesús are uKꞌojol ri Dios kachꞌeken na puꞌwiꞌ ri jastaq rech uwachulew.
\p 
\v 6 Ri Jesucristo xpe cho ri uwachulew, rumal ri jaꞌ xuqujeꞌ kikꞌ; man xaq xwi taj rumal ri jaꞌ xane rukꞌ kikꞌ xuqujeꞌ jaꞌ. Are ri Uxlabꞌixel kaqꞌalajisan we jastaq riꞌ, rumal chi ri Uxlabꞌixel are qas tzij.
\v 7 Oxibꞌ ri keqꞌalajisanik pa ri kaj.
\v 8 Koxchal junam kechomanik: ri Uxlabꞌixel, ri jaꞌ xuqujeꞌ ri kikꞌ.
\v 9 We kaqakoj ri kakibꞌij ri achyabꞌ, la are kꞌu mat kaqakoj ri uqꞌalajisanik ri Dios ri sibꞌalaj nim, jeriꞌ rumal chi are ri Dios kuya qꞌalajisanik chirij ri uKꞌojol.
\v 10 Ri winaq ri kakojon che ri ukꞌojol ri Dios kukꞌamawaꞌj we qꞌalajisanik riꞌ. Ri man kukoj ta ri Dios, tajin kubꞌij chi ri Dios xaq bꞌanal tzij, rumal cher man kukoj taj ri qꞌalajisanik ri xuya ri Dios chirij ri uKꞌojol Jesús.
\v 11 Ri qꞌalajisanik ri xubꞌan ri Dios are chi ri Dios xuya jun alik qakꞌaslemal, ri kꞌaslemal riꞌ kꞌo pa ri ukꞌojol Jesús.
\v 12 Ri winaq ri xkojon che ri Kꞌojolaxel Jesús kꞌo ukꞌaslemal. Ri man kojoninaq ta che ri Kꞌojolaxel, maj ukꞌaslemal.
\s1 Kꞌisbꞌal rech we wuj
\p 
\v 13 Kintzꞌibꞌaj we jastaq riꞌ chiꞌwe, ri ixkojoninaq che ri uKꞌojol ri Dios. Rech xa jeriꞌ kiwetaꞌmaj chi kꞌo jun alik ikꞌaslemal.
\p 
\v 14 We kujqebꞌ rukꞌ ri Dios chutayik jun jastaq ri are urayibꞌal ukꞌuꞌx, areꞌ kujuto. Are waꞌ ri kꞌulibꞌal qakꞌuꞌx ri kꞌolik.
\v 15 We qetaꞌm chi ri Dios kuta ri qachꞌawem, rajawaxik kakubꞌiꞌ qakꞌuꞌx chi kꞌo chi qukꞌ ri kaqata che.
\p 
\v 16 We kꞌo jun karil ri rachalal kubꞌan jun makaj ri man rech ta kamikal, chubꞌana chꞌawem puꞌwiꞌ rech kaya na ukꞌaslemal rumal ri Dios. Are tajin kinbꞌij jun ri kubꞌan mak ri man kakꞌaman ta bꞌik pa kamikal. Kꞌo jun makaj ri kakꞌaman bꞌik pa kamikal, man kinbꞌij ta in chi utz kabꞌan chꞌawem puꞌwiꞌ ri winaq ri kubꞌan we mak riꞌ.
\v 17 Ronojel uwach etzelal makaj, pune jeriꞌ, kꞌo kꞌut makaj ri kakꞌaman bꞌik pa kamikal.
\p 
\v 18 Qetaꞌm chi ri winaq ri xkojon che ri Cristo man kꞌo ta chik pa mak, xane katoꞌik rumal ri Jesucristo uKꞌojol ri Dios xuqujeꞌ man kachap ta chik rumal ri Itzel.
\p 
\v 19 Ri uj qetaꞌm chi uj ralkꞌwaꞌl ri Dios, are kꞌu ri winaq ri man e kojonelabꞌ taj e kꞌo chuxeꞌ raqan uqꞌabꞌ ri Itzel.
\p 
\v 20 Qetaꞌm kꞌut chi ri uKꞌojol ri Dios xpetik chuyaꞌik qetaꞌmabꞌal rech jeriꞌ kaqetaꞌmaj uwach ri kꞌaslik Dios. Qas uj kꞌo wi rukꞌ ri uKꞌojol Jesucristo. Are waꞌ ri kꞌaslik Dios, xuqujeꞌ are jun alik kꞌaslemal.
\v 21 Loqꞌalaj taq walkꞌwaꞌl, man kiqꞌijilaꞌj taj ri e bꞌanom taq tyox.
